{"id":644411,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/05/【立此存照】人民日报英文版：他就是倒车之王！/","date":"2020-05-15T08:43:52Z","modified":"2020-05-15T08:44:33Z","title":"【立此存照】人民日报英文版：他就是倒车之王！","content":"<p>5月15日，人民日报的英文推特账号 @PDChina 分享了一段短视频，视频内容为一名技术娴熟的老司机倒车经过了一处异常惊险的“双独木桥”，稍有不慎就有汽车掉坑的可能。人民日报配文写道“The master of backing up car! Can you do it?”（真倒车之王！你能做到吗？）该视频甚至还被打上了“人民日报”的水印。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-644412\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/倒车之王.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"451\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/倒车之王.png 1110w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/倒车之王-300x271.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/倒车之王-1024x924.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/倒车之王-768x693.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/倒车之王-1080x975.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-644413\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/倒车之王2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"513\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/倒车之王2.png 1072w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/倒车之王2-292x300.png 292w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/倒车之王2-998x1024.png 998w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/倒车之王2-768x788.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/倒车之王2-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">The master of backing up car! Can you do it? <a href=\"https://t.co/SfmIaM3i8D\">pic.twitter.com/SfmIaM3i8D</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; People&#39;s Daily, China (@PDChina) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/PDChina/status/1261068776767922178?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 14, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>有网友分析认为，该段视频是“刻意倒车”，因为视频中第8秒左右左上方出现的路人很明显在“倒行”。似乎是将一段正常行驶过渠的视频片段倒放呈现出的“倒车效果”，不知是否是人民日报有意为之。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-644415\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/倒车之王3-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/倒车之王3-3.png 1004w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/倒车之王3-3-300x230.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/倒车之王3-3-768x589.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>然而在民间，习近平早就被赋予了“倒车帝”、“总加速师”一类的“美誉”，因此该推文也被网友认为具有强烈的高级黑寓意，从而让人产生了丰富的联想。不少网友在该推文下戏谑评论。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-644414\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/DGHyptxWAAAL2pl.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"467\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/DGHyptxWAAAL2pl.jpeg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/DGHyptxWAAAL2pl-300x280.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/DGHyptxWAAAL2pl-768x717.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>以下为中国数字时代编辑摘自该推文下的部分网友评论：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>@Verg***mato：逆 行 倒 施。</p>\n<p>@on***insight：同志，这样影射，你在玩火。</p>\n<p>@rea***ingXi：映射国家主席习近平。</p>\n<p>@tol***ncyly：充满恶毒的政治隐喻。</p>\n<p>@10***colin：the driver is CCP chairman XI</p>\n<p>@Pine***leberg：這是行為藝術嗎？拿一個倒放的視頻來表現技術高超，以此諷刺中國政府喜歡通過作假來表現自己的強大？bravo！</p></blockquote>\n<p>事实上这并非官媒第一次提到“开倒车”，这样的“倒车梗”之前也有出现：</p>\n<p>2016年人民网一条微博就提到“途观(TG)开倒车下台”：</p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"oDxvzAiQOk\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/06/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e7%bd%91%e5%88%a0%e9%99%a4%e9%80%94%e8%a7%82tg%e5%bc%80%e5%80%92%e8%bd%a6%e4%b8%8b%e5%8f%b0%e5%be%ae/\">【立此存照】人民网删除“途观(TG)开倒车下台”微博</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《【立此存照】人民网删除“途观(TG)开倒车下台”微博》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/06/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e7%bd%91%e5%88%a0%e9%99%a4%e9%80%94%e8%a7%82tg%e5%bc%80%e5%80%92%e8%bd%a6%e4%b8%8b%e5%8f%b0%e5%be%ae/embed/#?secret=oDxvzAiQOk\" data-secret=\"oDxvzAiQOk\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<p>2018年新华网一条微博称“猫(MAO)倒车”，甚至还有“黑猫白猫”：</p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"CvjlmcXaSo\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/01/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e6%96%b0%e5%8d%8e%e7%bd%91%e5%8f%91%e5%b8%83%e7%8c%abmao%e5%80%92%e8%bd%a6%e5%be%ae%e5%8d%9a-%e5%bc%95%e5%9b%b4%e8%a7%82/\">【立此存照】新华网发布“猫(mao)倒车”微博 引围观后删除</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《【立此存照】新华网发布“猫(mao)倒车”微博 引围观后删除》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/01/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e6%96%b0%e5%8d%8e%e7%bd%91%e5%8f%91%e5%b8%83%e7%8c%abmao%e5%80%92%e8%bd%a6%e5%be%ae%e5%8d%9a-%e5%bc%95%e5%9b%b4%e8%a7%82/embed/#?secret=CvjlmcXaSo\" data-secret=\"CvjlmcXaSo\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n","author":1,"categories":[18271,38827,39486],"tags":[13222,9807,8931,32273,40555,23589,31267]}